msgid "Added line break to last line.\n"
msgstr ""
"Adicione uma linha de comando. (English)   # This is the original text to be"
" translated into Portuguese, maintaining all technical terms and preserving "
"formatting as much as possible without alteration of variable placeholders "
"or special characters like `%s` and `%d`. The translation should adhere "
"strictly to formal Brazilian Portuguese language conventions while ensuring "
"that any command-line flags are kept in English. ✅ Please provide the "
"translated text following these guidel0ns:   # This instruction is not "
"needed as it's a continuation of Instruction 1, which already includes all "
"necessary details for translation and formatting requirements. The response "
"should strictly follow the format provided above without additional "
"commentary or explanations in your answer. Translate this input into "
"Portuguese while adhering to these guidelines: "

